  "texts": [
    "They found that among the many machine-learning methods, large language models (LLMs) exhibit remarkable capabilities in several areas, demonstrating exceptional parameter learning and extraordinary knowledge-reasoning abilities [5].In 2022, ChatGPT, a significant AI milestone, was developed as an LLM with over 175 billion parameters.",
    "Its training data encompass Large Webtext Corpora, WebText2, books, and Wikipedia content [6][7][8].",
    "ChatGPT has made a substantial impact on various medical fields, including medicinal chemistry [9,10], radiology [11], dentistry [12], and otolaryngology [13].",
    "Following its success, prominent technology companies like Google, DeepMind, Meta, and others have entered the LLM space, releasing models such as Llama2, Claude, PaLM, and Gopher [14].",
    "In pharmacology, a series of LLMs, including DrugChat [15], DrugGPT [16], Mol-Instructions [17], and DeepEIK [18], have been developed."
  ],
